de instrumenten van de cultuur --

00:16:51.000 --> 00:16:52.610
godsdiensten, recht,

00:16:52.610 --> 00:16:55.360
handel, kunst, wetenschap, technologie.

00:16:55.360 --> 00:16:57.210
